Create an IAM ROLE for EC2 and attach a policy name AmazonEC2RoleforAWSCodeDeploy so that EC2 can access or connect with Code Deploy agent. This will be used in ec2 instance.
Create and IAM Service Role and attach a policy  AWSCodeDeployRole policy with CodeDeploy permissions that grants AWS CodeDeploy access to your target instances.  THis will be used in CodeDeploy service role.


We will be using Code Deploy Code Commit and Code Pipeline
